data.description: Discover this inviting single family home with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and original hardwood floors in the living and dining areas. The main level boasts a charming fireplace, while the lower level features a family room, 4th bedroom, 3rd full bath and another fireplace. New carpet graces the bedrooms and lower level, with a modern kitchen showcasing a new refrigerator and stove top. Enjoy comfort year-round with a recently installed HVAC system and energy-efficient windows. An attached garage, a lovely backyard, and a new sewer lateral complete the package. Top-rated schools and easy access to shops, parks, and transportation make this a must-see. Title is open with Old Republic Title. Escrow officer is Kathy Gilginas, Escrow number is 1713026945-KG
